Description:
  Adapter-aware migration generator for RailsKit.

  Generates the appropriate migration file based on the configured
  database adapter in railskit.yml (or the --adapter override).

  Adapters:
    postgresql  → Standard ActiveRecord migration (db/migrate/)
    supabase    → Raw SQL migration (db/supabase_migrations/)
    convex      → TypeScript schema stub (db/convex_schemas/)

Example:
  rails generate migration CreateProducts name:string price:decimal

  With postgresql adapter:
    db/migrate/20260304120000_create_products.rb

  With supabase adapter:
    db/supabase_migrations/20260304120000_create_products.sql

  With convex adapter:
    db/convex_schemas/create_products.ts

  Override adapter:
    rails generate migration CreateProducts name:string --adapter=supabase
